WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Arroway' is a Workbench game based on the sliding tiles
puzzles, but in this game you have to move or turn arrows so that
3 arrows are lined-up and point in the same direction. As arrows
are lined up, they disappear, leaving empty tiles and you get
points... if the arrows are all of the same colour, the better it
is...

  As the game progress, 'jewels' will appear on empty tiles, if 3
arrows point towards a jewel, you get more points...

  Have fun!

